MovieRating_KNN<-function(userId,itemId,n,K){
  
  #n
  sub<-which(data$userid==userId)
  if(length(sub)>=n){
    sub_n<-sample(sub,n)
  } else {
    sub_n<-sample(sub,length(sub))
  }
  
  known_itemid<-data$itemid[sub_n]
  unknow_itemid<-itemId
  
  #
  unknow_sub<-which(data$itemid==unknow_itemid)    
  user<-data$userid[unknow_sub[-1]]
  
  
  #
  data_all<-matrix(0,1+length(user),2+length(known_itemid))
  data_all<-data.frame(data_all)
  
  names(data_all)<-c('userid',paste('unknow_itemid_',itemId),paste("itemid_",known_itemid,sep=""))
  
  item<-c(unknow_itemid,known_itemid)
  
  data_all$userid<-c(userId,user)
  
  
  #data_all 
  for(i in 1: nrow(data_all)){
    data_temp<-data[which(data$userid==data_all$userid[i]),]
    for(j in 1: length(item)){
      if(sum(as.numeric(data_temp$itemid==item[j]))!=0){ #
        data_all[i,j+1]<-data_temp$rating[which(data_temp$itemid==item[j])]
      }
    }
  }
  
  
  data_test_x<-data_all[1,c(-1:-2)]
  data_test_y<-data_all[1,2]
  
  data_train_x<-data_all[-1,c(-1,-2)]
  data_train_y<-data_all[-1,2]
  
  
  fit<-knn(data_train_x,data_test_x,cl=data_train_y,k=K)
  
  l<-list("data_all"=data_all,"True Rating"=data_test_y,
          "Predict RAting"=fit,"UserID"=userId,"ItemID"=itemId)
  return(l)
}

p<-''
length<-20
diff<-0
for(Item in 1:20){
  result<-MovieRating_KNN(userId = 1,itemId = Item,n = 50,K=10)
  p<-c(p,paste("userid:",result$`UserID`,",True Rating:",result$`True Rating`,",predict rating",result$`Predict RAting`))
  diff<- diff + abs(as.integer(result$`True Rating`)-as.integer(result$`Predict RAting`))
}

transferMatrix_withoutD<-function(G){
  for(i in 1:nrow(G)){
    n<-length(which(G[i,]!=0))
    G[i,]<-G[i,]/n
  }
  return(G)
}

getRank<-function(G,iter=10){
  n<-ncol(G)
  # 
  x<-rep(1/n,n)
  for(i in 1 : iter){
    x<- G %*% x
  }
  return(x)
}

transferMatrix_withD<-function(G,d=0.85){
  cs <- colSums(G)
  cs[cs==0] <- 1
  n <- nrow(G)
  delta <- (1-d)/n
  A <- matrix(delta,nrow(G),ncol(G))
  for (i in 1:n) A[i,] <- A[i,] + d*G[i,]/cs
  return(A)
}
